this_title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Demons of the Past

玩具熊的午夜后宫：来自过去的恶魔
introduction: Eight years after Mike Schmidt ventured out to stop child serial killer, William Afton, his presence has fallen silent, and no one can find him. Since then, Afton's legacy continues to spark terror. Night guard new comers Dwight and Jessica fall into a pit hole when they decide to take matters into their own hands and it's up to them to bring an end to the Afton regime
